{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"44301198b2","title":"中学教师的右派言论（四）","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（四）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编印，1957年11月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e4d9afaa69","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"44301198b2"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0fa7d3988d","name":"山西"},{"id":"55e168a906","name":"王耀辰"},{"id":"a7f2fb4c98","name":"田中五"},{"id":"c884edf972","name":"郑泽夫"},{"id":"f153063f81","name":"牟乃标"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7cd0bc5671","type":"title","text":"中学教师的右派言论（四）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"44301198b2"},{"id":"8e9bb4f19c","type":"authors","text":"山西王耀辰田中五郑泽夫牟乃标","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"44301198b2"},{"id":"0051745ef7","type":"paragraph","text":"王耀辰（阳泉二中教师）：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"44301198b2"},{"id":"8459282210","type":"paragraph","text":"“学校是清一色的领导，党团员当家，民主人士有职无权。党在各级部门中要民主人士，不过是作作配搭”。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"44301198b2"},{"id":"d91838de7a","type":"paragraph","text":"田中五（祁县中学教师）：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"44301198b2"},{"id":"335bd587a5","type":"paragraph","text":"“知识分子是一盘散沙，民盟是知识分子的政党，要和共产党争领导”。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"44301198b2"},{"id":"8d32d18f0d","type":"paragraph","text":"郑泽夫（榆次一中教师、民盟盟员）：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"44301198b2"},{"id":"b3f05e642e","type":"paragraph","text":"“民主党派如没有政治自由、地位平等、组织上的独立，就成了共产党的附属机构”。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"44301198b2"},{"id":"58140ddb0b","type":"paragraph","text":"牟乃标（临汾一中教师）：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"44301198b2"},{"id":"ec35cc505e","type":"paragraph","text":"“共产党和民主党派不是领导和被领导的关系，而应该是对等的关系，民主党派和共产党应平立平坐，资产阶级和无产阶级应联合专政，资产阶级和无产阶级共同进入社会主义”。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"44301198b2"}],"page":{"id":"d3f9175f0c","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"44301198b2","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}